column_description: The field "administrative_division_category" records the category of the city, such as a municipality directly under the central government, sub-provincial city, prefecture-level city, league, etc
column_description_CN: 字段"administrative_division_category"记录这个城市的类别，分别为"直辖市"、"副省级市"、"地级市"、"盟"等

column_description: The field "POP2020" records the population of the city in 2020
column_description_CN: 字段"POP2020"记录这个城市2020年的人口数量

column_description: The field "POP2010" records the population of the city in 2010
column_description_CN: 字段"POP2010"记录这个城市2010年的人口数量

column_description: The field "POP2000" records the population of the city in 2000
column_description_CN: 字段"POP2000"记录这个2000年的人口数量

column_description: The field shape records the location of the city
column_description_CN: 字段"shape"记录这个城市的位置

column_description: The field "Shape_Length" records the perimeter of the city
column_description_CN: 字段"Shape_Length"记录这个城市的周长
